==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surprisal
<hw>Sur*pris"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Surprise</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>The act of surprising, or
state of being surprised; surprise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How to secure the lady from <qex>surprisal</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Because death is uncertain, let us prevent its
<qex>surprisal</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surprise</ent>⟦br⟧
